# NexusAI Website Overview

The NexusAI website is a modern landing page for a fictional AI company. The site is built with HTML, CSS (Tailwind), and JavaScript.

## Main Files
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - The main HTML file containing the entire website structure
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project documentation

## Website Structure
The website is organized into several key sections:
1. Navigation bar
2. Hero section with animated terminal
3. Client logos section
4. Solutions section showcasing AI agent products
5. Technology section highlighting technical capabilities
6. Stats section with key metrics
7. About section with company information
8. CTA (Call to Action) section
9. Contact form section
10. Footer with site links and copyright information

